verbose_text: The positive controls were quercetin (25 muM) and dexamethasone (2.5 nM) in the analysis of expression of NF-kappaB1 and COX-2; N G -monomethyl-L-arginine (L-NMMA) as inhibitor of NO-syntase (100 muM); zileuton as inhibitor of 5-LOX (5 muM); indomethacin and NS-398 (N-[2-(Cyclohexyloxy)-4-nitrophenyl] methanesulfonamide) as inhibitors of COX-1 and COX-2 (1.25 muM and 5 muM, respectively).
